Interface CrimeDataLoadingListener<Result>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CrimeActivityBase, CrimeDetailActivity, CrimesListActivity, CrimeSummaryActivity, UtvarDetailActivity

    public interface CrimeDataLoadingListener<Result>
    CrimeDataLoadingListener is an interface used to listen for certain crime data loading events.

    Tom
